title: Air Strike
description: Air Strike is a strategic rocket warfare game where you need to destroy all your enemies. Navigate two challenging stages of gameplay. In Stage 1, take control of a powerful rocket and strategically target personal stockpiles and enemies. Stage 2 puts you in command of an elite squad, tasked with eliminating all opposition. Engage in intense battles with tanks, helicopters, and more. With realistic 3D graphics, experience lifelike battles and explosive combat. Your mission's success relies on your tactical prowess. Prepare for victory, commander!
